### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

###

### Verify email with OTP (replace OTP with actual code from email)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

###

### Resend OTP if expired
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

### Login after email verification
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get user profile (replace TOKEN with actual JWT token from login)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Update user profile
PUT http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith"
}

###

### Forgot password
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

### Reset password with OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "otp": "123456",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

###

### Test basic app endpoint
GET http://localhost:3000
